  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 - \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Violation of Foreign Exchange Guidelines Strong Action - Central Bank of Sri Lanka",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "In the current situation where the country is facing a massive economic crisis, all parties related to the economic structure should bear its burden equally. Accordingly, with the goal of advancing the country's welfare and moving forward, all the issues related to foreign currency exchange, export restrictions, etc., which have already been announced, will be closely monitored and it will be ensured that they are followed accordingly.",
        "The Central Bank of Sri Lanka has announced that strict action will be taken against those who violate the law.",
        "The Government and the Central Bank are jointly taking various measures to reduce the impact on the people of the country as a result of the current economic crisis.",
        "The main reason for the current crisis and its further intensification is the very low level of liquid foreign reserves in the country's banking system. The decline in foreign reserves has impacted imports of essential commodities including fuel.",
        "In such a background, the central bank is in a position to impose certain restrictions on the income from exports to ensure that the country's banking system has sufficient foreign reserves.",
        "In particular, measures were taken to control the outflow of foreign currency by imposing restrictions on exports and the period of payment by the Central Bank, and measures were also taken to encourage foreign currency inflow through licensed banks through informal mechanisms.",
        "However, the success of these regulatory and regulatory measures depends on the support and cooperation of the business community and the banking sector.",
        "However, it has been brought to the attention of the Central Bank that some parties in the market are not following these guidelines. All parties are expected to bear the burden equally during a very difficult period.",
        "Accordingly, the Central Bank would like to reiterate to all parties related to the economy that all matters related to foreign currency exchange guidelines, export restrictions will be closely monitored and ensured that they are properly followed in order to prioritize the interest of the country and move forward for all of us. Violators will be subject to strict action as per applicable law.",
        "At the same time, the negotiations with the International Monetary Fund with the aim of obtaining an economic assistance program have shown some progress and debt restructuring activities are being carried out with the help of qualified legal and financial advisors, the report said."
      ],
